WEBVTT

01:58.000 --> 02:01.160
Kill everyone but the children.

02:02.480 --> 02:03.640
Don't go there!

02:07.640 --> 02:08.560
Don't go there.

02:53.080 --> 02:54.040
Mother!

02:58.720 --> 03:00.000
Mother!

03:02.360 --> 03:03.640
Mother!

03:05.000 --> 03:05.920
Stop!

03:40.040 --> 03:41.320
You wear painted skins?

03:43.080 --> 03:45.000
You're not from the Shilin Sect.

03:49.000 --> 03:50.560
Who are you exactly?

03:51.400 --> 03:52.720
What are you after?

04:41.320 --> 04:44.280
The Frost Spell. The Formless Moon Sect.

04:52.440 --> 04:53.440
Wu Wangyan?

05:05.800 --> 05:10.240
You always wanted to know
what secret I was hiding.

05:11.440 --> 05:13.520
Now you have your answer.

05:26.880 --> 05:27.720
The Star Stone…

05:30.000 --> 05:31.000
Give it back!

05:32.920 --> 05:34.040
Dream on.

05:57.080 --> 05:58.280
The sachet…

06:06.040 --> 06:07.320
Oh no!

06:47.920 --> 06:52.080
Threatening me with him won't work.
I can't undo the petrification.

06:53.600 --> 06:54.720
I can't do it.

06:54.800 --> 06:56.400
Then I'll kill him!

07:05.040 --> 07:07.280
The stone thorn has my runes on it.

07:07.880 --> 07:09.560
If I cast the spell…

07:11.000 --> 07:12.280
you'll die instantly.

07:13.720 --> 07:18.160
Do you choose death,
or do you help me free my people?

08:00.960 --> 08:02.280
Qing Yi!

08:20.480 --> 08:22.040
The Dragon Deity's Power.

08:29.720 --> 08:31.280
You have it,

08:32.400 --> 08:34.400
so why no dragon birthmark?

08:36.120 --> 08:37.000
The Dragon clan…

08:39.280 --> 08:40.159
Birthmark…

08:42.840 --> 08:44.760
Your birthmark is so interesting.

08:44.840 --> 08:46.040
It looks like a heart
made of flowing water.

08:46.920 --> 08:48.040
<i>How did I never see it?</i>

08:53.160 --> 08:54.720
You're not Wu Wangyan.

08:55.560 --> 08:57.000
You're not her!

08:58.800 --> 09:01.240
You're looking for a child
with a dragon birthmark.

09:04.120 --> 09:05.920
Then I know who you are.

09:07.360 --> 09:08.600
That's right.

09:09.680 --> 09:10.880
She's Jiu Ying.

09:32.720 --> 09:33.960
Little Nine.

09:34.640 --> 09:35.760
Or maybe…

09:37.600 --> 09:39.600
I should call you by your true name…

09:43.640 --> 09:44.480
Jiu Ying.

09:55.240 --> 09:56.880
Who sent you here?

09:56.960 --> 09:58.520
Why pretend to be a Shilin Sect member?

09:59.280 --> 10:00.880
It… It's Jiu Ying.

10:00.960 --> 10:02.400
You know of me?

10:03.440 --> 10:06.320
The first time I saw
those nine spots on you,

10:07.560 --> 10:09.080
I suspected it was you.

10:10.440 --> 10:13.080
Those nine markings on your head
are quite pretty.

10:13.160 --> 10:15.960
So I'll call you Little Nine.

10:16.880 --> 10:21.680
Later, you found out
we weren't the real Man Man and Di Zhu.

10:22.280 --> 10:23.840
If you were dead,

10:25.000 --> 10:30.680
those two demons
who possess Man Man and Di Zhu

10:31.480 --> 10:33.240
would never get the Star Stone.

10:34.000 --> 10:36.680
The only one who could stay by us
and eavesdrop on our every word

10:37.600 --> 10:38.840
was Little Nine.

10:39.680 --> 10:43.640
But Little Nine
was just an ordinary, harmless snake.

10:43.720 --> 10:47.040
Relax. The blood didn't turn dark.

10:47.800 --> 10:51.680
So, I had to wait for you to slip up,
to reveal your true form.

10:52.280 --> 10:53.960
I failed twice…

11:09.280 --> 11:11.720
but in the end, I caught you.

11:12.360 --> 11:16.400
Just a bit too late,
since you've grown your third head.

11:18.640 --> 11:21.000
I don't quite understand
what you're saying.

11:22.160 --> 11:25.880
But it sounds like you know me well,

11:27.080 --> 11:28.920
like an old friend.

11:30.600 --> 11:31.720
Indeed.

11:33.280 --> 11:34.200
Very well.

11:36.600 --> 11:38.440
All your scheming,

11:39.520 --> 11:41.920
just to get a look at my true form?

11:42.000 --> 11:45.920
Because in the end,
you'll become the Demon King,

11:46.560 --> 11:50.240
destroying the whole world,
yet no one knows your origin.

11:51.120 --> 11:56.800
So, I wanted to find out
what exactly you are.

12:00.520 --> 12:01.800
In the beginning,

12:03.080 --> 12:05.240
I was just a snake egg

12:05.320 --> 12:08.560
buried in this earth
for millions of years, unable to hatch.

12:08.640 --> 12:10.720
The egg was filled with deadly venom.

12:10.800 --> 12:15.240
<i>The Aodeng people migrated here</i>
<i>and were poisoned one after another.</i>

12:15.320 --> 12:16.760
<i>They thought it was a plague.</i>

12:19.160 --> 12:22.040
Then the Star Stone fell from the sky,

12:22.120 --> 12:23.800
<i>bringing heavenly fire.</i>

12:28.680 --> 12:31.800
The heat of the flames hatched you.

12:32.800 --> 12:36.560
I broke out of my shell,
absorbed the Star Stone's power,

12:36.640 --> 12:37.840
and became a demon.

12:38.480 --> 12:40.120
The egg disappeared.

12:40.200 --> 12:41.920
The Aodeng people
stopped getting poisoned.

12:42.680 --> 12:46.680
They thought it was a blessing
from the Star Stone.

12:47.920 --> 12:49.360
After I hatched,

12:50.040 --> 12:54.600
the first person I saw was Di Zhu.

13:05.400 --> 13:08.640
<i>But I was newly born, my power weak.</i>

13:08.720 --> 13:12.400
<i>I could only take Di Zhu's blood</i>
<i>and briefly possess her.</i>

13:13.600 --> 13:17.840
That way, I could go
into the cave every night

13:17.920 --> 13:21.280
to absorb the Star Stone's power
and grow stronger.

13:22.560 --> 13:25.160
To keep others from getting the Stone,

13:26.200 --> 13:27.760
you started killing.

13:29.000 --> 13:33.680
The Star Stone's power
gave me a second venomous head.

13:34.720 --> 13:39.120
I smeared venom on a hairpin
to kill those who coveted the Stone.

13:39.720 --> 13:41.360
But the venom couldn't kill demons.

13:42.400 --> 13:43.480
So…

13:45.240 --> 13:46.760
I could only frame you.

13:47.440 --> 13:51.040
Too bad you didn't succeed.

13:53.360 --> 13:54.480
True.

13:56.440 --> 13:58.720
But I got something unexpected.

14:00.400 --> 14:04.840
I found a power source
even stronger than the Star Stone.

14:05.600 --> 14:06.600
Killing.

14:07.360 --> 14:10.080
No, not killing. It's fear.

14:11.440 --> 14:14.760
I realized, the more people died,

14:14.840 --> 14:16.800
the more the Aodeng people feared,

14:17.840 --> 14:19.520
the stronger I became.

14:22.240 --> 14:24.000
In just a few days,

14:26.640 --> 14:28.760
I've already grown my third head.

14:31.360 --> 14:33.400
Even without the Star Stone,

14:34.200 --> 14:36.760
as long as the world
is filled with despair,

14:37.680 --> 14:40.840
fear, and hatred,

14:41.440 --> 14:43.760
I'll have an endless supply of power.

14:44.680 --> 14:45.920
Soon enough,

14:46.800 --> 14:51.080
all nine of my heads will be fully grown.

14:56.120 --> 14:58.600
With all nine heads,

14:58.680 --> 15:02.120
Jiu Ying can break each head
into nine spirit fragments.

15:02.200 --> 15:05.200
Eighty-one pieces
scattered across the world.

15:05.280 --> 15:08.480
That's why this land
is overrun with people

15:09.080 --> 15:10.760
controlled by Jiu Ying.

15:11.360 --> 15:14.840
The Six-Eyed Butterflies under Jiu Ying
planted pupae inside us.

15:14.920 --> 15:16.520
We have no choice but to obey.

15:16.600 --> 15:19.280
Wu Zhiqi was already going
to give the Star Stone to Jiu Ying,

15:19.360 --> 15:21.560
to bring it to the battlefield
and destroy humanity.

15:22.160 --> 15:26.400
Why control you
and arrange for us to steal it?

15:28.120 --> 15:31.800
Because… the Star Stone
wasn't meant to destroy humanity.

15:32.480 --> 15:35.640
It was to make humans
and demons destroy each other.

15:35.720 --> 15:36.800
What?

15:38.120 --> 15:40.960
The Yuan Clay Incident,
which sparked the war,

15:41.040 --> 15:42.120
seemed like an accident,

15:42.200 --> 15:43.880
but it was also schemed by Jiu Ying.

15:47.720 --> 15:49.520
You mean Yuan's death

15:51.400 --> 15:52.640
wasn't an accident?

15:53.280 --> 15:54.480
It wasn't just him.

15:55.000 --> 15:55.960
There are countless others

15:56.040 --> 15:59.080
you'd never suspect
possessed by Jiu Ying's spirit.

15:59.160 --> 16:00.800
They walk among us,

16:01.520 --> 16:05.560
constantly stirring conflict
between our races, igniting battles.

16:05.640 --> 16:11.360
And all this strife and hatred
makes Jiu Ying stronger.

16:11.440 --> 16:13.280
She even slaughtered the nine Dragons.

16:15.920 --> 16:18.520
No wonder they say
Jiu Ying can't be killed.

16:18.600 --> 16:21.880
Turns out, even sealed
by the nine dragon sons,

16:22.440 --> 16:23.960
you're still causing chaos.

16:25.000 --> 16:30.760
They thought sealing my nine heads
would destroy me for good.

16:30.840 --> 16:31.720
Too bad

16:32.800 --> 16:36.240
I'd already scattered countless
spirit fragments across the world.

16:36.840 --> 16:41.840
<i>Each piece can attach to a living being.</i>

16:50.320 --> 16:52.080
Once it attaches,

16:52.160 --> 16:54.200
it waits for a moment
when the host's mind wavers,

16:54.280 --> 16:55.480
then takes control.

16:55.560 --> 16:59.880
As long as one piece remains,
Jiu Ying cannot die.

16:59.960 --> 17:01.680
You might as well give up.

17:02.960 --> 17:04.720
No. You're wrong.

17:05.720 --> 17:08.280
The Dragon Deity
will defeat Jiu Ying in the end.

17:09.160 --> 17:12.920
All 81 spirit fragments
will be destroyed one by one.

17:13.520 --> 17:15.240
That annoying Shilin Sect

17:15.839 --> 17:19.640
has been hunting for my spirit fragments.

17:19.720 --> 17:21.680
I have to kill Chi Wen,

17:22.280 --> 17:23.800
break the seal,

17:25.079 --> 17:26.920
and get my heads back.

17:27.960 --> 17:31.120
So you've been searching
for the dragon's descendants.

17:32.160 --> 17:33.640
Because only a dragon…

17:34.800 --> 17:36.040
Can kill a dragon.

17:41.880 --> 17:43.960
The Six-Eyed Butterflies
gave us the glowing worm.

17:44.680 --> 17:46.840
Once it's inside the Star Stone,

17:47.440 --> 17:51.920
it will devour his insides,
make him lose control,

17:52.520 --> 17:54.160
and cause an explosion.

18:09.960 --> 18:11.320
Where's the Star Stone?

18:35.760 --> 18:38.960
What do we do now?
Where are we taking him?

18:39.040 --> 18:40.080
We can't go anywhere.

18:56.840 --> 18:58.120
The Six-Eyed Butterfly…

18:59.680 --> 19:00.920
is actually two people.

19:01.000 --> 19:02.080
That's right.

19:02.160 --> 19:08.000
Unlike you, we're inseparable,
loving brothers.

19:18.160 --> 19:19.080
Watch out!

19:28.000 --> 19:30.640
You've got it wrong. We're not with him.

19:31.320 --> 19:34.920
Threatening us with him won't work.
You should just kill him.

19:36.840 --> 19:37.880
Are you sure?

19:38.680 --> 19:42.240
The look on the person
behind you says otherwise.

19:43.320 --> 19:46.080
If you don't want him dead, come with us.

19:57.200 --> 20:00.680
Don't forget he imprisoned you
for all those years.

20:03.480 --> 20:06.960
You said earlier he secretly helped us

20:08.280 --> 20:09.880
by letting me go.

20:14.080 --> 20:15.480
All these years,

20:16.520 --> 20:20.440
in that tiny space, he was my only friend.

20:30.120 --> 20:32.120
If you no longer care
about the Star Stone,

20:32.760 --> 20:35.480
then why did you attack me at the wedding?

20:44.600 --> 20:47.920
-Kiss!
-Kiss!

20:55.120 --> 20:56.400
Come out, Little Nine!

20:57.040 --> 20:58.600
I simply wanted you dead.

21:14.480 --> 21:15.800
Tian Di!

21:30.440 --> 21:32.760
Let Wu Zhiqi go! Stop!

21:58.480 --> 22:02.840
You're covered in wounds,
yet you can't bear to hurt her.

22:03.640 --> 22:05.200
How devoted.

22:05.800 --> 22:09.440
Let's see how long you can last.

23:13.280 --> 23:14.560
Don't be rash!

23:22.520 --> 23:24.840
Oh no. He's losing control of his power!

23:35.840 --> 23:37.720
Tian Di… No!

23:41.400 --> 23:42.640
Yuan Xizai!

24:14.000 --> 24:16.160
So this is the Star Stone
exit Master Bai Ze mentioned?

24:16.240 --> 24:17.680
This stone tablet?

24:18.600 --> 24:19.840
It's Wu Shiguang's master's grave.

24:19.920 --> 24:22.320
Stop bickering. Quick, smear the blood.

24:22.400 --> 24:23.240
Okay. Got it.

24:23.920 --> 24:25.440
Wu Shiguang would be surprised

24:25.520 --> 24:28.120
that the keepsake of our friendship I kept
would save his life years later.

24:57.320 --> 24:58.800
Why isn't it working?

24:59.520 --> 25:00.720
That liar Bai Ze!

25:04.080 --> 25:06.280
Are they really going to die
in the disasters?

25:37.320 --> 25:39.520
Master… What's happening?

25:40.200 --> 25:41.600
Father!

25:42.840 --> 25:43.760
Mother!

25:43.840 --> 25:44.920
Shiguang!

26:02.440 --> 26:04.760
Quick, take him and go!

26:04.840 --> 26:07.520
I won't! I have to save my parents!

26:07.600 --> 26:08.600
Father!

26:25.720 --> 26:27.440
What are you waiting for? Go after them!

28:17.280 --> 28:18.280
Lu Wuyi!

28:24.560 --> 28:25.560
Lu Wuyi!

28:41.000 --> 28:43.080
-Oh no.
-What's happening to Wu Zhiqi?

28:43.760 --> 28:45.960
The third head, the head of frenzy.

28:46.720 --> 28:50.160
It drives a person mad,
making their demon power run wild.

28:53.920 --> 28:57.520
If Wu Zhiqi loses control,
it'll cause the Hurricane Catastrophe.

28:59.440 --> 29:01.080
I've figured out Jiu Ying's origin.

29:01.160 --> 29:03.520
Let's go. We'll use
the Star Stone to leave.

29:04.440 --> 29:05.320
-Okay.
-Let's go.

29:06.880 --> 29:08.120
Where's the Star Stone?

29:23.760 --> 29:27.480
You go first.
You can turn into sand and leave.

29:29.360 --> 29:30.520
Let's go together!

30:17.760 --> 30:19.680
<i>Once we get the Star Stone,</i>

30:19.760 --> 30:22.960
<i>we can use our power</i>
<i>to leave the illusion.</i>

30:49.640 --> 30:50.800
You…

30:57.120 --> 30:58.240
He…

30:59.840 --> 31:03.440
He's Yuan Wuhuo, the butterfly demon.

31:05.160 --> 31:06.120
He went in too?

31:07.120 --> 31:09.600
When the Star Stone's pull
was strongest earlier,

31:10.440 --> 31:12.040
I almost got sucked in.

31:20.720 --> 31:23.240
The butterfly demon hiding
in the shadows pushed me away.

31:23.760 --> 31:26.080
But he got pulled in himself.

31:27.440 --> 31:30.920
So, in the past they're living in,

31:32.680 --> 31:35.240
who is the true owner of that time?

31:35.320 --> 31:39.800
That past was shared by the two brothers.

31:40.400 --> 31:43.680
They are both the owners
and witnesses to each other.

31:45.880 --> 31:47.600
You're not that Yuan Wuhuo.

31:48.680 --> 31:50.640
You're the butterfly demon, Yuan Wuhuo.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.200
That's right.

31:54.920 --> 31:57.000
So you've been acting this whole time.

31:58.760 --> 31:59.600
That's right.

32:00.440 --> 32:02.720
How else could I make you
lower your guard,

32:02.800 --> 32:04.400
help me get the Star Stone,

32:05.360 --> 32:06.880
and leave this place?

32:08.160 --> 32:10.600
So you were behind it before too.

32:12.160 --> 32:13.080
Exactly.

32:14.280 --> 32:16.520
<i>I tried to kill Tian Di</i>

32:17.800 --> 32:19.720
to turn him back into the Star Stone.

32:20.520 --> 32:22.040
But it didn't work.

32:22.760 --> 32:26.840
All that struggling was pointless.

32:48.720 --> 32:50.520
Did you really think

32:52.160 --> 32:53.640
I was your brother?

32:55.440 --> 32:56.600
Aren't you?

32:57.640 --> 32:58.560
No.

33:01.120 --> 33:03.400
Then why do you look exactly like me?

33:04.560 --> 33:05.840
You're wrong.

33:08.600 --> 33:10.480
Know your place.

33:11.560 --> 33:13.440
You look like me.

33:15.560 --> 33:16.560
I…

33:24.680 --> 33:26.560
Who am I?

33:29.000 --> 33:31.120
You'll never know.

33:35.120 --> 33:36.920
Stay here forever.

34:23.400 --> 34:24.679
Yuan Xizai!

34:33.360 --> 34:34.800
<i>Why did I lose my power?</i>

34:34.880 --> 34:36.360
<i>Quick, heal him!</i>

34:36.440 --> 34:37.679
<i>Hurry!</i>

34:37.760 --> 34:39.679
<i>Xizai! Xizai!</i>

34:40.360 --> 34:42.719
<i>Save him! Save him!</i>

34:57.720 --> 34:59.040
I can't hold it together much longer.

34:59.560 --> 35:03.440
The Star Stone must not shatter.
I still need it to save my people.

35:04.040 --> 35:05.320
Is there any way?

35:06.080 --> 35:06.920
Yes.

35:07.000 --> 35:08.480
What is it?

35:10.080 --> 35:11.280
What is it?

35:12.120 --> 35:13.360
The Dragon Deity's Power.

35:14.280 --> 35:17.400
It can restore anything
and bring the dead back to life.

35:27.400 --> 35:28.920
Dragon hearts as one,

35:29.800 --> 35:31.360
all to source return,

35:32.760 --> 35:34.280
all barriers break!

36:07.760 --> 36:09.320
Dragon hearts as one,

36:10.160 --> 36:11.600
all to source return,

36:12.280 --> 36:13.800
all barriers break!

36:45.280 --> 36:48.960
Master Jiu Ying truly has
flawless foresight.

36:53.160 --> 36:57.240
<i>I infused my demonic energy</i>
<i>into a fragment of the Star Stone.</i>

36:57.840 --> 37:01.080
<i>Once it joins with the piece Wu Zhiqi has,</i>

37:01.160 --> 37:04.840
<i>the entire Star Stone</i>
<i>will shatter completely.</i>

37:06.360 --> 37:09.200
<i>Wu Zhiqi will surely sacrifice himself,</i>

37:09.280 --> 37:12.280
<i>releasing</i>
<i>the Dragon Deity's Power to fix it.</i>

37:12.360 --> 37:15.320
<i>Then you'll have your chance</i>
<i>to seize his power.</i>

37:54.600 --> 37:55.920
Give up.

37:56.640 --> 38:01.200
Take after Xiaowei,
and you'll share her fate.

38:16.960 --> 38:22.680
Bai Ze, you already gave 70% of your power
to that false Dragon Deity.

38:23.280 --> 38:27.160
And you used another 20%
to fix the Star Stone.

38:27.760 --> 38:32.040
With the 10% left,
you want to break my barrier?

38:32.640 --> 38:34.400
What a joke.

38:38.160 --> 38:39.480
Or maybe…

38:42.080 --> 38:44.600
you could try using
the Dragon Deity's Power.

39:04.440 --> 39:05.920
Now we're really trapped here.

39:06.640 --> 39:07.800
It's all my fault.

39:09.040 --> 39:11.400
It's all my fault. I'm sorry.

39:13.840 --> 39:17.880
At least we know Jiu Ying's origin,
that's something.

39:17.960 --> 39:22.120
And we found out something else,
even better.

39:22.760 --> 39:23.840
What's it?

39:24.640 --> 39:26.040
Jiu Ying's weakness.

39:27.840 --> 39:29.320
What's his weakness?

39:30.440 --> 39:32.120
The same weakness as mine.

39:35.240 --> 39:36.600
Look out!

39:39.160 --> 39:41.640
Ji Ling! Ji Ling!

39:44.280 --> 39:47.360
Ji Ling! Hold on to me! Don't let go!

39:51.200 --> 39:52.480
Lu Wuyi!

39:57.600 --> 39:58.720
What are you doing?

40:02.880 --> 40:04.000
A spike will help…

40:16.320 --> 40:20.880
When disaster strikes,
lovers stay together.

40:24.080 --> 40:27.400
<i>"Live together, die together"?</i>
<i>That's just a story to fool girls.</i>

40:28.000 --> 40:32.160
I don't like him enough to die for him.

40:43.600 --> 40:44.480
The Star Stone!

40:49.520 --> 40:50.400
Let go!

40:51.280 --> 40:52.240
No!

40:52.840 --> 40:54.240
Let go of the other hand!

40:54.840 --> 40:57.400
Take out the spike! Trust me!

41:04.240 --> 41:05.440
Let's take a gamble.

41:06.360 --> 41:08.360
If we lose, we just stay here.

41:09.640 --> 41:10.640
And I'll marry you!

42:46.720 --> 42:47.800
You're here.
